/etc--->editable test configuration
/etc we have
1.system configuration files
2.service configuration files
3.user & authentication config
4.secutiy configs


/etc/passwd-->user information
ex--> if we create user that user details will store in /etc/passwd
if we want to update password /etc/shadow

/etc/ssh
main file /etc/ssh/ssh_config


